{"tid":819472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"潮玩 crossover 大白兔奶糖要出潤唇膏","createTime":"2018-09-14T22:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T03:36:21.000Z","uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9482bbc8236dc5cc6bcb9dc9999e0a34edc979","tid":819472,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T22:37:16.000Z","msg":"老品牌跨界 大白兔奶糖要出潤唇膏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/063610_9dbfcb278030bb333f4bb573a23c40de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F063610_9dbfcb278030bb333f4bb573a23c40de.png&h=75023590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(截圖：網絡)<br />\n大家小時候常吃的零食大白兔奶糖，如今要出潤唇膏！大白兔奶糖生產商，中國老品牌冠生園食品，將於另一歷史悠久的國貨品牌，日用化學品公司美加淨，推出聯名款產品--美加淨大白兔奶糖味潤唇膏。消息一出，網上未賣先火！<br />\n<br />\n根據中國《新華網》報道，上海知名老字號冠生園食品，是在這個月較早前，在一個博覽會上，公佈這一消息。<br />\n<br />\n這款奶糖味潤唇膏包裝設計近日已流出。從包裝上看，和大白兔奶糖幾乎一模一樣，只是在左上角加了美加淨的標誌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據《21世紀經濟報道》，這款奶糖味潤唇膏，包裝上將延續大白兔奶糖的經典形象，主要成分為乳木果油、橄欖油、甜杏仁油等食品級植物精華，融入牛奶精華，經過調香，在滋潤雙唇的同時，保留大白兔奶糖的經典味道。<br />\n<br />\n潤唇膏即將推出的消息，很快就引起眾多網友期待。有網友已經在幻想擦上這款潤唇膏的體驗：「彷彿已經聞到了甜甜的奶香。買了大概不是塗完的是吃完的！」<br />\n<br />\n還有網友甚至希望這個聯名，接著會推出護手霜、身體乳，「塗了就變成一隻行走的甜甜大白兔啦！」<br />\n<br />\n據瞭解，美加淨大白兔奶糖味潤唇膏，9月20日會在美加淨的天貓旗艦店開賣。<br />\n<br />\n- CH8/WL"},{"pid":"45d2478a988154e35b09e4d88c8eb6dbb720dc1c","tid":819472,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T22:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/063824_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F063824_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=d408bf0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n解放軍 crossover starwar"},{"pid":"1f0fcb425ac40a2c330dc6dd0771de7b13b4b756","tid":819472,"uid":72280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45d2478a988154e35b09e4d88c8eb6dbb720dc1c","tid":819472,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T22:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/063824_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F063824_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=d408bf0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n解放軍 crossover starwar"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T22:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/064050_f87549d19860be1bf26ed7e0781227c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F064050_f87549d19860be1bf26ed7e0781227c6.png&h=34348aa5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dc60d8238f67a15edf910e3139dca1c0b7224f0","tid":819472,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T22:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/064117_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F064117_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=8bb6237f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/064124_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F064124_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d8f808d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本自衛隊 crossover 鋼dum"},{"pid":"a66695ace03e38723f3ae150d059759c98be18f5","tid":819472,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}